**Key Activities**:
- Implement in distinct phases
- Build core architecture and interfaces first
- Add main functionality incrementally
- Implement integration points with other components
- Write comprehensive test suite
- Create detailed component documentation

**Example Commands**:
```bash
# Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/new-component

# Run specific phase tests
pytest tests/unit/test_component_core.py
pytest tests/unit/test_component_functionality.py
pytest tests/integration/test_component_integration.py

# Check test coverage
pytest --cov=src/component tests/ --cov-report=term-missing
```

